。二人認為香港市民應抵制任何破壞法紀、損及和平及暴力傷害他人的行為，並呼籲所有人應以克己、理性、和平的手法表達意見；又指通過國安立法可令社會早日恢復秩序，人人都可安居樂業。"},{"pid":"20e8d4a4df59dcb9190f4dbe7bf8af8f2d92ee53","tid":2047474,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦 耶撚 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"a4ec47087a597c0c3a16df5c872efddbd9b2f90b","tid":2047474,"uid":143474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:44:00.000Z","msg":"基督教好多呢啲仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而天主教好似少啲"},{"pid":"bd538738b714d2b8282091b37518506ee7d02a3c","tid":2047474,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:44:43.000Z","msg":"循道衛理同北區好鄰舍都係好人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d780ca5d00712fe2f0c390e73535cd28432b2c0b","tid":2047474,"uid":227835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"宗教團體咪又係利益團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難聽d講就係合法詐騙集團"},{"pid":"f6959627fb5220596276b1120378f0fd1bb009cf","tid":2047474,"uid":24131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d780ca5d00712fe2f0c390e73535cd28432b2c0b","tid":2047474,"uid":227835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"宗教團體咪又係利益團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難聽d講就係合法詐騙集團"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"部份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有部分仲出聲同反抗緊<br />\n聖公會就。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 紅到黑"},{"pid":"159967d008e7e2129dff8409d6520332430217c7","tid":2047474,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"你呢d耶教外國勢力<br />\n立完國安法第一樣就係批鬥你地啦"},{"pid":"f6397d094e8dbdf18e6e02a48e3fbb646cb343f6","tid":2047474,"uid":16250,"like":0,"d